'''三钛酸钠'''是一种无机化合物，化学式[[钠|Na<sub>2</sub>]][[钛|Ti<sub>3</sub>]][[氧|O<sub>7</sub>]]。它可以由[[二氧化钛|二氧化钛]]和[[碳酸钠|碳酸钠]]在高温下的反应制备。<ref>Fotiev, A.A.; Bobrova, A. M. Mechanism and kinetics of interaction between titanium dioxide and sodium carbonate{{ru}}. ''Issled. v Obl. Khim. i Tekhnol. Mineral'n. Solei i Okislov, Akad. Nauk SSSR, Sb. Statei'', 1965. 248-253. CAN65: 43090.</ref>它在[[盐酸|盐酸]]中进行离子交换，可以得到H<sub>2</sub>Ti<sub>3</sub>O<sub>7</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the Ceramic Society of Japan|volume=124|issue=6|language=en|issn=1348-6535|date=2016|pages=710–713|doi=10.2109/jcersj2.16022|url=https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/jcersj2/124/6/124_16022/_article/-char/ja/|title=Soft chemical synthesis and crystal structure of novel hydrogen titanium oxide H2Ti12O25|accessdate=2020-06-15|author=Kunimitsu Kataoka, Junji Akimoto|archive-date=2018-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180602185626/https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/jcersj2/124/6/124_16022/_article/-char/ja/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

